One thing I found

This code works in Chrome, failed in Edge without any error (Didn't test on Firefox, Safari at that time)

```js
const f = new File([arrayBuffer], file.name, { type: file.contentType });
saveAs(f);
```

This code works in Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge

```js
const b = new Blob([arrayBuffer], { type: file.contentType });
saveAs(b, file.name);
```

Hope it helps.

