```
class examples.Bar(luigi.Task):
    num = luigi.IntParameter(key_field=True)
    other = luigi.IntParameter()

    def run(self):
...

    def output(self):
....

```
This way we delegate the use to inform which luigi Params are the one that matter for identifying the class.

